  "solution": {
    "answer": "$H_0(N_k) \\cong \\mathbb{Z},\\quad H_1(N_k) \\cong \\mathbb{Z}^{k-1} \\oplus \\mathbb{Z}/2,\\quad H_2(N_k) = 0,\\quad H_n = 0 \\text{ for } n \\geq 3.$",
    "steps": [
      "CW structure: one 0-cell $v$, $k$ 1-cells $a_1, \\ldots, a_k$ (all loops at $v$), one 2-cell $e$ with word $a_1^2 \\cdots a_k^2$.",
      "$d_1 = 0$ (all generators are loops). $d_2(e) = (2, 2, \\ldots, 2) \\in \\mathbb{Z}^k$.",
      "$H_2 = \\ker(d_2: \\mathbb{Z} \\to \\mathbb{Z}^k)$. Since $e \\mapsto (2,\\ldots,2) \\neq 0$, $d_2$ is injective, so $H_2 = 0$.",
      "$H_1 = \\mathbb{Z}^k / \\langle (2,2,\\ldots,2) \\rangle$. Change basis: $f_i = a_i - a_{i+1}$ ($i=1,\\ldots,k{-}1$) and $f_k = \\sum a_i$. Then $d_2(e) = 2f_k$.",
      "In the new basis: $H_1 = \\mathbb{Z}^{k-1} \\oplus (\\mathbb{Z}/2)$, generated by $f_1, \\ldots, f_{k-1}$ freely and $f_k$ with $2f_k = 0$.",
      "Checks: $k=1$ ($\\mathbb{R}P^2$): $H_1 = \\mathbb{Z}/2$. ✓ $\\quad k=2$ (Klein bottle): $H_1 = \\mathbb{Z} \\oplus \\mathbb{Z}/2$. ✓"
    ]
  },
